# Rally core

- React Native 0.83 bare + Expo SDK 55, Supabase, React Navigation
- All Supabase calls via `src/services/` — never from components
- Env via `src/constants/config.ts` (react-native-config), never hardcode secrets
- Firebase messaging is lazy-loaded — do not init at module top level
- Android: no `watchPosition`; use expo-location patterns in `locationService.ts`
- Android 13+: request `POST_NOTIFICATIONS` before FCM token
- Styling: `src/constants/theme.ts`, existing components in `src/components/`
- Run `npm run verify` before PRs

See also: `CLAUDE.md`, `.cursorrules` (legacy pointer)
